bad times never last. strong people last. so know when it’s time to pick yourself up and get yourself going again. 👏🏼😤
 
something i asked @leftf0otforward to do for this video for @chrisjcheung ’s series “while i’m here” was to fall as many times as possible because I wanted to capture the act of perseverance. having to get over this mental hurdle of…
 
can i do it?
 
will i do it?
 
what’s the point of doing it?
 
will i succeed?
 
do you want to keep sitting in the same spot? or do you want to get to somewhere better?
 
i can say with 100% certainty that i want to get to somewhere better. we hope this encourages anyone out there afraid to take that first step forward to try. 🖤
being content with failing is a big part of me. i fail a lot and i learn a lot from it. 📠
